Dialogue: 1,0:00:10.07,0:00:11.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(352,388)\fsp-1}唯一看清真相的就是
Dialogue: 1,0:00:11.59,0:00:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(352,388)\fsp-1}小孩的外貌但頭腦是大人
Dialogue: 1,0:00:13.28,0:00:14.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(352,388)\fsp-1}他就是「名偵探柯南」！
Dialogue: 1,0:02:11.65,0:02:12.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(352,388)\fsp-1}開到另一個死路了
